MasterChef Canada - Season 2, Episode 9




Good Things in Small Packages

MasterChef USA judge Graham Elliot presents the home cooks with the smallest Mystery Box in MasterChef Canada history, filled with tiny proteins, vegetables, and greens. The home cook who wins the challenge receives an advantage in the Elimination Challenge, choosing which live underwater creature their fellow competitors have to cook with.




Original Air Date: 12-Apr-2015
